This paper focuses on identifying source code properties that correlate with defective infrastructure as code (IaC) scripts, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. The paper also involves analyzing defect-related commits and constructing defect prediction models, which could fall under programming languages (cs.PL), cryptography and security (cs.CR), software development (cs.SD), and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
